input_text.Prompt: Can you tell me how to see page likes on facebook?
input_text.Response A: Sure, I can tell you.  I don’t have a facebook account, but I’ve read about it online.  You should click on the “like” button to like a page.  Then, if you go to the page, you should see the number of likes next to the “like” button.
input_text.Response B: Sure! I’m happy to help you. If you go to your profile page and click on the “Like” button, you can see the people who like your page.
